description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 Vocaloid songs, navigators, and avatars!
Cover version songs by popular VTubers "Omaru Polka" and "Tsunomaki Watame" are also included!

This pncludes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Bless Your Breath / WADATAKEAKI
・Because You’re Here / PinocchioP
・Hatsune Creation Myth / cosMo@Bousou-P *Locked
・FUTURE EVE / sasakure.UK
・TODAY THE FUTURE / HarryP
・Singularity / keisei
・BEAT SYNCER / DIVELA
・Darling Dance / Kairiki bear *with cover version by Omaru Polka
・Cinderella / DECO*27
・God-ish / PinocchioP *with cover version by Tsunomaki Watame

■Navigator
・Hatsune Miku (MM 2018) *with voice
・Hatsune Miku (MM 10th) *with voice

■Avatar
・MUKU(2D, Magical Mirai 2018)
・MUKU(2D, Magical Mirai 2019)
・MUKU(2D, Magical Mirai 2020 Summer)
・MUKU(2D, Magical Mirai 2021)
・MUKU(2D, Magical Mirai 10th)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 7
